<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1907/506309-625x351.jpg" alt="Capfin reaps rewards of partnering with HelloFCB+" width="625" height="351">Not only did its first collaboration with the agency go from pitch to market in an extraordinarily swift five weeks, judging by the incredible uptake in applications, it really hit its mark proving that HelloFCB+’s Human Connections Agency mantra is much more than just industry hype.<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1907/506310-625x351.jpg" alt="Capfin reaps rewards of partnering with HelloFCB+" width="625" height="351">“We are delighted with the outputs from HelloFCB+ given the tight deadlines the agency had to meet,” said Capfin Brand Campaign Manager, Louise White. “And, even more importantly, that business results have exceeded all expectations. We look forward to working on our next campaign with the HelloFCB+ team.”<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1907/506311-625x351.jpg" alt="Capfin reaps rewards of partnering with HelloFCB+" width="625" height="351">The omni-channel campaign, which includes television commercials; print, press and radio ads; an array of digital and social executions; and digital out-of-home, is aimed at an aspiring and professional audience.It clearly demonstrates that Capfin, with its easy online and mobile application process, is always there for you, no matter where you find yourself, both in life and location. “By first creating a detailed map of the complete decision-making journey, we are able to strategically connect the right message with our audience at the right place and time,” said HelloFCB+ Chief Creative Officer, Mike Barnwell. <img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1907/506312-625x351.jpg" alt="Capfin reaps rewards of partnering with HelloFCB+" width="625" height="351">Executive Business Director, Lesley-Anne van der Nest, added: “In these tough economic times, it’s never been more important to ensure that efficiency and effectiveness work hand in hand, and our approach is really making sure that they do.”